# Funding

The project was funded by the [KdFS](https://www.kdfs.de), which allowed me to pay the performers and license the fonts used. Hendrik Kempt refused to be paid for his collaboration.

Additionaly was supported through a scholarship by the HAB from the [HfMA](https://www.hfmakademie.de/).

